4) Industrial & Scientific: The paper mentions the material and construction of the gun case, which could be of interest to individuals in the industrial or scientific fields who require durable and protective cases for their equipment.

5) Office Products: The paper mentions an adjustable carrying strap and leather trim, which could be relevant to individuals looking for professional or functional carrying cases for their work-related items.

Note: The provided categories are based on the information given and may not be exhaustive or completely accurate.
